defaultand a means to ensure
default the
defaultir
default dec
defaultisions
default are lawful. 
defaultThe Government’s proposals will significantly restrict access to judicial reviews, preventing people from using a vital tool to protect their basic human rights when public bodies act unlawfully or exceed their legal powers. 
default&#xa0;
defaultJudicial 
defaultr
defaulteview helps test th
defaulte compatibility of public decision making with rights under 
defaultEuropean Community Law and the Human Rights Act which enacted the European Convention on Human Rights (ECHR) into UK legislation. 
